results.content:
I don't think from this course that someone would gain the knowledge to start using Maven. For one thing it does not walk through step by step in a real world scenario how to start using Maven. It is more of a very quick series of lectures on different capabilities, but there is nothing that ties the course together. 
It seems to assume that you already have Maven knowledge so the title of the training is quite misleading.
